{"tid":981622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇科學家一世都冇研究成果？","createTime":"2019-01-14T12:20:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T12:32:25.000Z","uid":64694,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ded65cf203011b8d7a4c18cb02894f15d0a05d1c","tid":981622,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T12:20:20.000Z","msg":"研究咗一世，點知最後都冇任何嘅研究成果呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢哋會唔會怨恨自己踏上科學家呢條路？<br />\n<br />\n我記得以前有個科學家話研究緊一樣嘢，但研究緊嘅時候，已經諗唔到點樣研究落去，到咗樽頸位卡住咗，之後佢煮麵嗰陣突然諗到不如煮吓啲血漿，之後就得咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n【當科學遇上醫療】一碗即食麵破解 血漿基因的秘密 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpweekly.com/culture/cu0001/20170612-36217\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpweekly.com%2Fculture%2Fcu0001%2F20170612-36217&d=TXUNqOKSaOu0L9ZIy7QkrIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=0d147045\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpweekly.com/culture/cu0001/20170612-36217</a>"},{"pid":"5f1bde5766359fe0c7118f5a36fac67a04b8766d","tid":981622,"uid":199162,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T12:22:06.000Z","msg":"應該好多<br />\n<br />\n但冇人識因為冇成果"},{"pid":"2bf42ff8db04bec0ba9bb7284f89c59aa369fedd","tid":981622,"uid":64694,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5f1bde5766359fe0c7118f5a36fac67a04b8766d","tid":981622,"uid":199162,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T12:22:06.000Z","msg":"應該好多<br />\n<br />\n但冇人識因為冇成果"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T12:22:37.000Z","msg":"真係慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5153ee9c2c1f9c8ca61926a9303b18f52302d51","tid":981622,"uid":185780,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T12:24:09.000Z","msg":"null result 也是findings"},{"pid":"773240f25d942ec575ac6641787ea0a4751b17ec","tid":981622,"uid":88428,"like":0,"disli